'''Timzerɣelt''' neɣ '''Timni''' ([[Assaɣ ussnan]]: '''Anisoptera''') d yiwen n [[adu-tfesna]] n [[aburɣes|yibureɣsen]] yeṭṭafaren [[tafesna (tasnudert)|tafesna]] n [[Timzerɣlin|tmzerɣlin]], tettwassen s tallet-is (seɛɛu-ines) i [[tiṭṭ tuddist|wallen tugtudmawin meqqren]] d sin n [[afriw|wafriwen]] ifrawanen ijehden, d tfekka ɣezzifen. Dɣa deg kra n tikwal yettili-d wemray (luɛaṛa) deg usemgirred gar n temzerɣelt yakk d [[taẓewt n tala|tiẓawin n tala]] (''Zygoptera'') acku ttemcabint deg [[Tasensileɣt|talɣa tamuṛfulujt]].<br/> 
Timzerɣelt tettumeggez seg [[Tagemra|yibureɣsen inegmaren]] ixataren acku tettett [[tadast|tadasin]] d yibureɣsen imeẓyanen niḍen am [[Izi n wexxam|yizi n wexxam]] d [[tizizwit|tzizwa]] d [[ageṭṭuf|ugeṭṭuf]] d [[arẓaẓ|yirẓaẓen]] d waṭas n [[talmest|telmas]] niḍen, maca drus kan n tikwal deg wanda i d-tettet [[aferṭeṭṭu|iferṭeṭṭa]]. Ɣas akken timzerɣelt tga d aburɣes anegmar, maca ula d nettat tezmer ad tettwičč sɣur n [[agṭiṭ|yigḍaḍ]] d [[tazermemmuyt|tzermemmuyin]] d [[amqerqur|yimqerqar]] yakk tmzerɣlin meqqren fellas.

Ibureɣsen-a ttilin deg yibaliɣen d igelmimen d timedwin d wuna. Llant wazal n 5680 n telmas yemgaraden n tmzerɣlin deg umaḍal.

